{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01ApnUjrRPaQbCufYx3A2pEA","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# Session Issues Log — 2026-03-21\n     2→\n     3→### 3-3-onboard-alias — create-story (2026-03-21T04:24Z)\n     4→\n     5→- **Previous sprint file collision:** An existing `3-3-bmad-parser-story-bridge-command.md` exists from a previous sprint's Epic 3. No conflict since new file uses `3-3-onboard-alias.md`.\n     6→- **Ambiguous AC3:** Epic says `codeharness onboard scan` should map to \"equivalent audit subcommand,\" but audit has no subcommands. Interpreted as deprecation warning + base audit run.\n     7→- **Risk: Old exports removal.** `onboard.ts` exports `getLastScanResult()`, `getLastCoverageResult()`, `getLastAuditResult()`, and `resetLastScanResult()`. Need to verify no external consumers before removing.\n     8→- **Risk: `onboard epic` subcommand has no audit equivalent.** Dropping silently may surprise users.\n     9→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"1c9a200e-72ec-477b-8ec4-6d2e01a30422","uuid":"7a4f2e34-8ace-4389-ac41-1d9452fd169d","timestamp":"2026-03-21T04:32:15.376Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/.session-issues.md","content":"# Session Issues Log — 2026-03-21\n\n### 3-3-onboard-alias — create-story (2026-03-21T04:24Z)\n\n- **Previous sprint file collision:** An existing `3-3-bmad-parser-story-bridge-command.md` exists from a previous sprint's Epic 3. No conflict since new file uses `3-3-onboard-alias.md`.\n- **Ambiguous AC3:** Epic says `codeharness onboard scan` should map to \"equivalent audit subcommand,\" but audit has no subcommands. Interpreted as deprecation warning + base audit run.\n- **Risk: Old exports removal.** `onboard.ts` exports `getLastScanResult()`, `getLastCoverageResult()`, `getLastAuditResult()`, and `resetLastScanResult()`. Need to verify no external consumers before removing.\n