t.ts` is a pass-through (`return result`) -- no-op function. Exists for symmetry with `formatAuditHuman()` but adds no value. Minor tech debt.\n\n**Coverage gaps:**\n- None for story scope. All changed files at 100% coverage, all 119 project files above 80% floor, overall 96.97%.\n\n**Architecture concerns:**\n- The non-null assertions (`fixStories!`) on lines 91-103 are safe given the control flow but make the code slightly fragile to future refactoring. A restructuring that moves JSON formatting into the fix-handling block would eliminate the need for these assertions. Not blocking.\n\n**Items sent back for re-development:**\n- None. All HIGH and MEDIUM issues fixed."}],"totalDurationMs":273454,"totalTokens":71467,"totalToolUseCount":47,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1733,"cache_read_input_tokens":68723,"output_tokens":1010,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":1733},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
