{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01BmTP1jsvqXxTFrs1Y34XRz","type":"tool_result","content":"The file /Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/.session-issues.md has been updated successfully."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"1c9a200e-72ec-477b-8ec4-6d2e01a30422","uuid":"8b257dc1-9931-4880-8ae8-40147d9ed52f","timestamp":"2026-03-21T04:37:26.646Z","tool_use_result":{"filePath":"/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/.session-issues.md","oldString":"- **console.log in shared handler:** audit-action.ts line 107 uses console.log directly. Story says \"Do NOT use console.log directly\" but formatAuditHuman() returns pre-formatted strings — wrapping in ok()/info() would double-prefix.","newString":"- **console.log in shared handler:** audit-action.ts line 107 uses console.log directly. Story says \"Do NOT use console.log directly\" but formatAuditHuman() returns pre-formatted strings — wrapping in ok()/info() would double-prefix.\n\n### 3-3-onboard-alias — code-review (2026-03-21T04:38Z)\n\n- **HIGH: Unsafe double type assertion** in audit-action.ts:86 — `as unknown as Record<string, unknown>` bypassed type safety. Fixed with spread operator.\n- **MEDIUM: Dead branch guard** in audit-action.ts:101 — `fixStories &&` always true at that point. Simplified to `else`.\n- **MEDIUM: NFR9 violation** — onboard.test.ts at 325 lines, compacted to 230.\n- **MEDIUM: Branch coverage gap** — missing test for `skipped: true` path. Added, now 100%.\n- **LOW (not fixed): console.log in audit-action.ts:111** — established codebase pattern, needs new `raw()` output utility to fix properly.\n- **LOW (not fixed): formatAuditJson() is pass-through no-op** — exists for symmetry only.\n- **Coverage: 96.97% overall, all 119 files above 80% floor, 2783 tests pass**","originalFile":"# Session Issues Log — 2026-03-21\n\n### 3-3-onboard-alias — create-story (2026-03-21T04:24Z)\n\n- **Previous sprint file collision:** An existing `3-3-bmad-parser-story-bridge-command.md` exists from a previous sprint's Epic 3. No conflict since new file uses `3-3-onboard-alias.md`.\n- **Ambiguous AC3:** Epic says `codeharness onboard scan` should map to \"equivalent audit subcommand,\" but audit has no subcommands. Interpreted as deprecation warning + base audit run.\n- **Risk: Old exports removal.** `onboard.ts` exports `getLastScanResult()`, `getLastCoverageResult()`, `getLastAuditResult()`, and `resetLastScanResult()`. Need to verify no external consumers before removing.\n- **Risk: `onboard epic` subcommand has no audit equivalent.** Dropping silently may surprise users.\n\n### 3-3-onboard-alias — dev-story (2026-03-21T04:31Z)\n\n- **audit-action.ts branch coverage 95.83%:** Two uncovered branches (lines 96, 101) in JSON fix output formatting. Covered by audit.test.ts but not onboard.test.ts — redundant since both delegate to same handler.\n- **Test file size:** onboard.test.ts is 325 lines vs estimated 100-150. Consistent with project norms (audit.test.ts is 407 lines).\n- **console.log in shared handler:** audit-action.ts line 107 uses console.log directly. Story says \"Do NOT use console.log directly\" but formatAuditHuman() returns pre-formatted strings — wrapping in ok()/info() would double-prefix.\n","structuredPatch":[{"oldStart":12,"oldLines":3,"newStart":12,"newLines":13,"lines":[" - **audit-action.ts branch coverage 95.83%:** Two uncovered branches (lines 96, 101) in JSON fix output formatting. Covered by audit.test.ts but not onboard.test.ts — redundant since both delegate to same handler."," - **Test file size:** onboard.test.ts is 325 lines vs estimated 100-150. Consistent with project norms (audit.test.ts is 407 lines)."," - **console.log in shared handler:** audit-action.ts line 107 uses console.log directly. Story says \"Do NOT use console.log directly\" but formatAuditHuman() returns pre-formatted strings — wrapping in ok()/info() would double-prefix.","+","+### 3-3-onboard-alias — code-review (2026-03-21T04:38Z)","+","+- **HIGH: Unsafe double type assertion** in audit-action.ts:86 — `as unknown as Record<string, unknown>` bypassed type safety. Fixed with spread operator.","+- **MEDIUM: Dead branch guard** in audit-action.ts:101 — `fixStories &&` always true at that point. Simplified to `else`.","+- **MEDIUM: NFR9 violation** — onboard.test.ts at 325 lines, compacted to 230.","+- **MEDIUM: Branch coverage gap** — missing test for `skipped: true` path. Added, now 100%.","+- **LOW (not fixed): console.log in audit-action.ts:111** — established codebase pattern, needs new `raw()` output utility to fix properly.","+- **LOW (not fixed): formatAuditJson() is pass-through no-op** — exists for symmetry only.","+- **Coverage: 96.97% overall, all 119 files above 80% floor, 2783 tests pass**"]}],"userModified":false,"replaceAll":false}}
